![Main features](https://imgur.com/7YVauDl.png)
<font size="2">Requires [Modern Industrialization](https://modrinth.com/mod/modern-industrialization), [Tesseract API](https://modrinth.com/mod/tesseract-api) and [Kotlin for Forge](https://modrinth.com/mod/kotlin-for-forge). You likely already have most of these!</font>

**Yet Another Industrialization! (YAI!)** is an addon for [Modern Industrialization](https://modrinth.com/mod/modern-industrialization) that adds miscelaneous machines items and more!

# YAI's ~~killer~~ joyful features

**Machine Remover:** A powertool that can instantly break machines in a single click at the cost of energy

**Large Storage Unit:** The multiblock energy storage you (might) have longed for! It's capable of connecting to its voltage and inferior;

**Arboreous Greenhouse:** A multiblock machine that produces logs and leaves. It shows the current recipe's tree in-game and has built-in support for 20+ mods!

**Dragon Egg Energy Siphon:** Generate energy through usage of Dragon's Breath and a Catalyst (the egg is part of the multiblock, naturally).

**Machine Diagnoser:** Newbie-friendly device that diagnoses common issues that might be preventing a machine from running;

**Storage Slot Locker:** Allows (un)locking all slots to/of a specific resource at once;

**Configurable Mixed Storage:** Storage block with 9 item and 9 fluid slots. Very useful in conjuction with AE2 Export buses!

**Cryogenic Precipitator:** Use Cryofluid to produce ice, snow and all of its variants;

... and shitpost food because it's funny
